ABOUT

Minimal DBLTEK/Hybertone GoIP receiver.

In this state allows to forward sms messages to specified email.

SETUP

pre-requisities:

Perl, curl

cpanm setup:

curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - App::cpanminus

dependencies setup:

cpanm Email::MIME
cpanm Email::Sender::Simple

USAGE

./goip-sms.pl port email_from email_to

GOIP SETUP

Configurations tab on the left:

SMS Sender: enable
SMS Server IP: ip address where goip-sms.pl is running
SMS Server Port: port specified in command line of goip-sms.pl
SMS Client ID: anything you want
Password: anything you want


BUGS & FEATURE REQUEST

